    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<h1>奮銳黨的西門</h1><p>有英文譯本在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:4\">馬太福音十章4節</a>和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:18\">馬可福音三章18節</a>中，將奮銳黨西門的翻譯為Simon the Cananean，<em>見</em><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"7679\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleBibleDictionary\">西門#5</span>。</p>",
